replies.body: Ahhhhh wow that's a pretty long queue timer. It looks like you're queueing for Twisted Treeline, which is a lot less popular sadly, so it can sometimes take awhile to find matches. You might have better luck trying Co-Op vs AI on Summoners Rift, or trying to queue up for Twisted Treeline Normals.
